{"tid":493644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國停收洋塑膠　英國垃圾將無處可去","createTime":"2017-12-08T16:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T17:24:27.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9fffa763c04e85f6f13c3886bb57f738fc1303","tid":493644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:53:54.000Z","msg":"中國停收洋塑膠　英國垃圾將無處可去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台】內地當局為了治理環境，大刀闊斧推行改革，當中包括限制外國廢料進口。新措拖引發漣漪效應，遠在歐洲的英國亦遭波及。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日電訊報》報道，中國將會在明年三月起停止塑膠廢料進口，英國的垃圾將無處可去。<br />\n<br />\n目前英國每年製造約54萬噸塑膠廢料，當中有近三分之二都是運往中國。中國作為全球主要的垃圾進口國家之一，一旦停收，其餘垃圾進口國，如越南及馬來西亞等亦無能力代為處理，大量的英國塑膠廢料將會無處可去。<br />\n<br />\n英國屆時很可能要將廢料運往本地的堆填區或焚化爐處理，處理成本將飆升。地方政府要繼續提供廢物處理服務，就要加稅彌補支出，或收取額外的垃圾處理費用。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾危機迫在眉睫，有環保團體認為現在是改革英國廢物處理政策的大好機會，政府應該趁機興建多些廢物處理設施，大力發展本土回收業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=246117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D246117&d=l4n5bHCFn6JX4ua1sAVs%2FJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=23d9a5bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D246117&h=aca88113\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=246117</a>"},{"pid":"3dbaeb3b7cdd0764b11aecfbbc48b36801caf29b","tid":493644,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"瑞典唔係向外國買垃圾發電咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110c388c28db0bdbce1ab2108dc80a09c6e75c73","tid":493644,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞典唔係向外國買垃圾發電咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n燒膠有毒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc166f90e68a582a1716ec0f55de7d796c31e21","tid":493644,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"816c2ad14970ea7c4a0b8b5c60e3616ad7033ec1","tid":493644,"uid":144282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國咁本事做咩唔靠美國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係本事先唔收垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0e3053fac0e5a9c404a1e502d98846bd22601e","tid":493644,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國咁本事做咩唔靠美國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係本事先唔收垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係本事先唔做世界垃圾崗囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c755aeca3c377ef2328c2b8ff8120df56c5bf3d","tid":493644,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"鍊住英國佬個春袋"},{"pid":"bad453bb3c4f8ae0a9244df0057a2ca4b4a4802e","tid":493644,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍊住英國佬個春袋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同稀土單野一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}